{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" proposes layout to add in your views a lonely checkbox, without labels, texts nor icons components."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If you want to use a checkbox with additional texts and icon, prefer instead ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Conforms To","kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"type":"conformsTo"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","kind":"attribute","text":"MainActor"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"Indicator-states","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Indicator states"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The checkbox indicator has three available states:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"selected"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": the checkbox is filled with a tick, the user has made the action to select the checkbox","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"unselected"}]},{"text":": the checkbox is empty, does not contain a tick, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the checkbox","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"indeterminate","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": like a prefilled or preticked checkbox, the user did not do anything on it yet"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In you are looking for a checkbox with only two possible values, refer to "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"level":2,"text":"Particular cases","type":"heading","anchor":"Particular-cases"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","type":"reference"},{"text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look-and-feel is implemented for that if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."}]},{"text":"Accessibility considerations","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note also the component must be instanciated with a string parameter used as accessibility label."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"It is a good pratice (at least) to define a label for a component without text for accessibility reasons. This label will be vocalized by "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}]},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The vocalization tool will also use, after the label, a description of the component (if disabled, if error context), and a fake trait for checkbox."}]},{"level":2,"text":"Cases forbidden by design","anchor":"Cases-forbidden-by-design","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component.","type":"text"}]}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Code samples","anchor":"Code-samples","type":"heading","level":2},{"code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an indeterminate state checkbox","    @Published var selection: OUDSCheckboxIndicatorState = .indeterminate","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, no error, not in read only mode","    OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate(selection: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\")","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, but is an error context","    OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate(selection: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true)","","    \/\/ Never disable an error-related checkbox as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate(selection: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"text":"Design documentation","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Design-documentation"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"See "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/23f1c1-checkbox","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"},{"style":"note","name":"Since","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.12.0"}]}],"type":"aside"}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudscheckboxindeterminate"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Structure","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents25OUDSCheckboxIndeterminateV","symbolKind":"struct","title":"OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","kind":"id